template: SELECT MIN(title.title) AS title_title, MIN(movie_companies.movie_id) AS movie_companies_movie_id FROM movie_companies, movie_info_idx, info_type, movie_info, person_info, title WHERE info_type.id = movie_info.info_type_id AND info_type.id = movie_info_idx.info_type_id AND info_type.id = person_info.info_type_id AND movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info_idx.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info.note LIKE %s AND person_info.note = %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000;
